Mage duraṅ 
 
 1
Nedar buru jolare siṛimi chi siruṅ.
Ginatai gohalaya ॥koṅ॥
Kana hapui siṛimi, kana hapui siruṅ,
Baleć misińtańe chana ginataḱ góloya $$॥koṅ॥2 
 
 2
Sasaṅ akan piḍingi re, sunum akan piḍingi re.
Bale misingtańe chana kitaṕ saṭao tan ॥koṅ॥
Nòcha re diku nhon, nhora nàṅkiravić mea.
Misińere murukuń nel senotea $$॥koṅ॥2 
 
 3
Káka sakam tinjar bonjar,
Chekan kili tana jam dinḍa nhapanum ॥koṅ॥2
Kili kam jagarè redo,
Nàńaḱ kili 2 teń kili misame ॥koṅ॥2 
 
 4
Hesaḱ mata 2 lena baḍi mata 2 lena (ṭhik somoe rege
Tuyumm seṭer akana) ॥koṅ॥2
Hesaḱ mata 2 chaba eana baḍi mata 2 chaba eana
Sama gea tuyumm bonḍo l akana ॥koṅ॥2
Nàle nòṛaḱ re tuyu seta menaḱć (hakaka bakaka tan
Tuyuć kakiṛimea) ॥koṅ॥2 
 
[2] 
 
 5
Misiń racha bakara kiṭuṕ akan tiru akana ॥koṅ॥2
Ṭapa ṭapa baduḍi, ṭapa gasar ket́ ॥koṅ॥2 
 
 6
Nimiṅ jeṭe nimiṅ lolo
Nen nùli sakam dona kana gasaroḱ ॥koṅ॥
Baleć kimin seṭer lena,
Nen nùli sakam dona kana gasaroḱ ॥koṅ॥ 
 
 7
Latar aete jugi Hon, chetan aete jugi hon. 
 "koe" koe te jugimm seṭer lena ॥koṅ॥2
Nègań goṛe menaḱć recha,
Nàpuiń goṛe menaḱć recha, 
 'koe, koyedo jugi nhonaḱ koedo nòmame $$॥koṅ॥2 
 
 8
Daḱ do daḱ do tetaṅiń tan,
Láć do Láć do rengećiń tana.
Nòkon kore dudulum daḱ do beṭaoḱa .koṅ.
Chimin saniṅ chimin jiliṅ,
Nòkon reja dudulum daḱ do beṭaoḱa ॥koṅ॥
Daḱ do beṭaoḱa metam,
Diri sút́, rugut́ sút́ daḱ do beṭaoḱa ॥koṅ॥2 
 
 9
Munḍa koaḱ racha re, santa koaḱ racha re,
Kuṭura chi muta riṛi hekena .koṅ.2
kana nhapui kuṭura, akana nhapui muta,
Munḍa kore talaṕ ṭaka riḍiṅ hekena ॥koṅ॥2 
 
[ 3] 
 
 10
Buru bitar mage, beḍa bitar mage,
Chikatere daṛachu nàyume let́a ॥koṅ॥2
Rutu rio 2 teń nàyume let́a ॥koṅ॥
Banam chẽo 2 teń nàyume let́a ॥ 
 
 11
Neder piṛi 2 taḱ kansari baṅ, kalai ba nerainelat́a $$॥koṅ॥2
Gonoṅ sati menaḱ rechalaṅ kea ruaaić ॥ 
 
 12
Nàben dona baleć bare,
Rutu tedo, banam tedo nèsum rasika ॥koṅ॥2
Rutu te do banam te kaben nàsuloḱ ॥koṅ॥ 
 
 13
Nègań, nàpuń menaḱ redo,
Baṛi daru lidi 2 sua riṅ ॥koṅ॥2
Nèngań, nàpuń bańać,
Baṛi daru lidi 2, doṛa he eana ॥koṅ॥2 
 
 14
Naben doja bale bareng,
Kenjar bonjar raja doben beṭa taya chi.koṅ.2
Beṭa ṛoliṅ beṭa taya,
Samaṛam ganḍu rinki rakaṕ akana ॥koṅ॥2 
 
 15
Buru mage chawahana, beṛa mage chaba hana,
Chigo chikan tewen tol gojena.koṅ.2 
 
[4] 

Niha tinge sanań,
Baṭa baṭi buru re baṭi gojen ben.koṅ.2 
 
 16
Nender buru jolare,
Jiki china, sarasanḍi manḍa rakaw let́a ॥koṅ॥
Akana napui jiki, akana napui sarasanḍi,
Bale bareń cha metam manḍa rakaṕ leṛa ॥koṅ॥ 
 
 17
Chia chia chepar Hon, chia chia guturahona.
Haga ko disu meh do bugi tana chia ॥koṅ॥
Sukuge bano, dukhuge
Maḍako bir kore ko bakaṛa tana ॥koṅ॥2 
 
 18
Nawen doja bale bareg, buru bitar reaṛi benaniro niriya,
Noro mata le redo, jangi mata le redo,
Mage rea dhoti doben kirĩya chi ॥koṅ॥2
Kawen kirĩya redo, kawen kejanay redo,
Naben geda balego barey disum tumio ॥koṅ॥ 
 
 19
Chetan pukhari chel chopol,
Latar pukari chel chola.
Baṅ lekan naku kiṅ rakaṕe lena ॥koṅ॥2
Jĩbiri menahḱ recha laṅ, jibiri koṭouṅ kiṅ ॥koṅ॥2
Raba mena recha laṅ, rawa koṭouṅ kiṅ ॥koṅ॥2 
 
 20
Bareng racha kadam daru,
Kadam daru chetanete da do joro tana ॥koṅ॥2 
 
 
[5] 

Daḱ do telae ben bareng,
Sona rupa tiṛite da, do telae ben ॥koṅ॥2 
 
 21
Jiṛim suku jan redo;
Boṛo rea baṛa napanum baṛa nemańe meh |k koṅ॥2
Jiṛi karem suku jan redo,
Boṛo rea baṛa napanum nalom nemaṅiaṅ ॥koṅ॥ 2 
 
 22
Chetano ko mag akana, lataro ko mag akana,
Nòkonare juṛilang mage misana ॥koṅ॥ 2
Mage misana lang juṛiṅ,
Bala saka nature lang mage misana ॥koṅ॥ 2 
 
 23
Munḍa ko racha kadam daru,
Jeṭe tichi lolate moyalan tana ॥koṅ॥ 2
Akana napui jeṭe te, akana napui lolate,
Samay bapui seno tanate, moyalan tan |k koṅ.॥ 2 
 
 24
Disumedo gule gule, raṅnachi do mele mele,
Disum kochi bareng ben niatintana |k koṅ.॥ 2 
 
 25
Naling doja bale bareng
Sirima jeṭe, note lolo riliaṅ ॥koṅ॥ 2
Naben doja bale bareng,
Mant́ ko bitar juṅbulae nubul rebena ॥koṅ॥ 2 
 
[ 6 
 
 26
Chetan pukhari, latar pukhari,
Maena moh nakukiṅ rakabelena ॥koṅ॥ 2
Nasulikiṅ ben go bareng,
Bugin 2 jagadare nasulikiṅ ben ॥koṅ ॥ 2
Gonoakiṅ ben go bareng,
Ikoisi baisi kore gonoakiṅ ben॥koṅ॥ 2 
 
 27
Buru bitar mage do, pata bitar mage do,
Dili kulaṅy ben go bareng, kaji kulaṅy ben ॥koṅ॥ 2
Kaben dili kulaṅy redo, kaben kaji kulaṅy redo,
Baṭa baṭi buru rea baṭi gojena ॥koṅ॥
Tole tole buru reṅa tol gojena ॥koṅ॥ 2 
 
 28
Niyang tikiṅ napung tikiṅ mena redo,
Chiṭi kireṅ maḍi, nutu dul akana ॥koṅ॥ 2
Niyang tikiṅ napui tikiṅ bang kiṅa,
Chiṭi ki re maḍi nutu noṭang eana ॥koṅ॥ 2 
 
 29
Chetan kunḍi, latar kunḍi
Doneha chi masala leko chenḍo tan
Akana napui donea, akana napui masala,
Bareng here beneṭa leko chenḍo tana ॥koṅ॥ 2 
 
 30
Nuli chuṭukay riya bareng
Nisir chenḍo do. 
 
[7] 

Jagada daaḱ riya bareng
Keḱ ye baṭa do.
Guli tuṭi menaḱ redo bareng,
Tuyanja lopoṅ tai mea bale bareng ॥koṅ॥ 2 
 
 31
Nengaṅe napuṅe mena redo,
Nuli ḍumasu ḍumwa, kuda ḍumasu ḍumba nuṅwal nerĩaḱ
Negaṅe napuṅe bangaya,
Nuli ḍumasu ḍumba, kuda ḍumasu ḍumba,
Numbul goyo natu ḍing ॥koṅ॥ 2 
 
 32
Nape disum do munḍa,
Dirisut́ bonj raja dado niji tan ॥ koṅ॥ 2
Nale disum do munḍa,
Pataa gasar jan redo dado ranjeḍo |k koṅ.॥ 2 
 
 33
Hatu kuṭi uli daru,
Meaḍege jo len esu siwila.
Mata somay hoao redo, jome samay hoao redo,
Kagajo sakame re ole kulaeṅ bena.
Kam ole kulaeṅ redo, kam dili kulaeṅ redo,
Baṭa baṭi buru reṅ baṭṭi gojena ॥
Heleke teke buru reṅ tol gojena ॥koṅ॥ 
 
 34
Kam toṭ akan reó, kam sangar ken reó,
Laṛata jilum nela rem tabu tabuya. 
 
[8] 

Nisai sarige chakat́ bano,
Laḍata jilum nela rem tabu tabuya ॥ koṅ॥ 
 
 35
Neang napuṅi ṭai kenare,
Bangali dhoti chaeṅ tega tegaya.
Neang napui bage kiḍing,
Seer lija botoe botoy akana ॥koṅ॥ 
 
 36
Mage paraṕ hoba lena,
Nen reching nu nua tehareṅ nu nua ॥koṅ॥ 
 
 37 
 Manḍi doko Manḍi tana, rebe rebe,
Nili doko chala tana choṭo choṭo,
Nicha baṛa juṛig do meḍe jolopi ॥koṅ॥2 
 
 38
Buddhi netoy-alaṅ misiṅ,
Chiṭhi miṭhi bangalare buddhi netoy alaṅ.
Buddhi neto kere misiṅ, diri lekan se laṭhilaṅ nobor ket́a ॥
Jaṭhi lekan kagajolaṅ nitir ket́a ॥
Buddhi neto kere misiṅ,
Nende nonol punḍi kagajo disum jari ket́ ॥koṅ॥ 
 
 39
Nam dona bareṅ negam menai,
Nam dona bare napum menai,
Sadae jor balego bareṅ, chatom numbul rem ॥koṅ॥
Naṅy dona bareṅ nengay bangae, 
 
[9] 

Naṅy dona bareṅ napuiṅ bagay,
Sadae jor balego bareṅ, jibon jeṭhe loloreh ॥koṅ॥
Naṅyonga nengay menay redo, naṅyoga naṅpui menay redo,
Sadae jor balego bareṅ jiwan chatom numbul reh ॥koṅ॥ 
 
 40
Neṭeḍińatanagoṅm bare, neṭheḍiń-tanama.
Mihaḍege misim tem neṭeḍiń-tana ॥koṅ॥
Chabuṛa taṅyawenago bareṅ chabuṛataṅy ben,
Gelebar doreare chabuṛataṅy ben ॥koṅ॥
Chapa natũi benago bareṅ, chapa natuiṅ ben,
Nilabaṛi kagajore chapa natuiṅ bena.
Meḍadaham joroy-hago bareṅ, meḍadaham joroyaha,
Chapa sakam nel kete meḍadaham joroyaha ॥ koṅ॥ 
 
 41
Buddhim neto tan go bareṅ,
Binihur nisikulareh buddhim ne to tana.koṅ.
Ṭibul bil akanago bareṅ,
aikorṭ bagaṅlare ṭibul bilakana.
Ṭiwul chetan rena bareṅ,
Sona reha kagajo bilanakah naha.koṅ.
Buddhim neto lereṅ bareṅ,
Sonareha pĩsilate nomworatuimeha.koṅ. 
 
 42
Chetan pukhari latar pukhari,
Napũi gecha roṛa let́ joṛa nuli bah.koṅ. Dhuḱ si0॥
Baṛay nasitan bareṅ, 
 
[ 10] 

Nede nende sepeṛet́ baṛay nasitan.koṅ. Siḱ dhu0 ॥
Baṛago nemaiḱ ben bareṅ,
Tiṛigo chetan biṛiteh baṛagoh nemaiwen.koṅ. Siḱ dhu0 ॥ 
 
 43
Surugo sutam dogo bareṅ gutuihalang,
Chigo bareṅ galaṅyalang.koṅ.
Buddhim neto tanago bareṅ,
Kumpani duhare buddhim netotana.koṅ.
Nisirakanagom bareṅ, suru sutam galaṅ hankan,
Nisira ka nam.koṅ. 
 
 44
Jeṭhe singi seṭher lena,
Koto koto baha lena jenga juṛi bah.koṅ. Dhuḱ si0॥
Ji, ge, soṛanago metam,
Mutuḍa mutuḍa ji, ge, lalacho.koṅ.siḱ dhu0 ॥ 
 
 45
Nengay napuiṅ ṭhai kena,
Gete gete senehor tala riliṅ ha ॥koṅ॥
Nengay napuiṅ baṅ kiha,
Gete gete senehor tisaratuḍĩh ॥ koṅ॥ 
 
 46
Gaṛako nasi ludam baṛa,
Chiminete misiṅ koben jagaray ha ॥koṅ॥
Gutui achim galaṅya,
Chiminete misiṅ koben kajiaya ha ॥koṅ॥ 
 
[ 11] 

Jahogeh metam jahogeh,
Niju seno ha ॥koṅ॥
Jahogeh metam jahogeh,
Jagaratũi ha ॥koṅ॥
Kajinatũi ha ॥koṅ॥2 
 
 47
Nengay napũi ṭhaikena,
Bir daru lekaṅy goḍhanakana ॥koṅ॥
Nengay napũi bangaya,
Mat́ buru mat́ sakam lekaṅy batarianah ॥koṅ॥ 
 
 48
Ḍinḍa redom jarama redom, napanum,
Boṛo redo napanum sunum jorotan ॥koṅ॥
Non nanam, noponanam,
Boṛo redo napanum tuḍunko tuka tan ॥koṅ॥ 
 
 49
Tataṅy tikiṅ, jihaṅy tikiṅ,
Chuḍhukiṅ bonga tan goṛe, sasang banoha ॥koṅ॥
Sasang nakiṅ namehan, buluṅ nakiṅ namehan,
Chuṭhu nagoy nirihan,
Nuḍũi boleahan ॥koṅ॥ 
 
 50
Nender buru reaṛi misingi jeṭhe tichi, lolote,
Nekelan tana |k koṅ॥
Akana napui jeṭhe, akana napui lolo,
Misiṅ go, laigo renge, dah go tentaṅ teh
Nekelan tana ॥koṅ॥ 
 
[ 12] 
 
 51 

Nendor piṛi piṛite,
Hoy ho chire; gama, dudugar tana ॥koṅ॥
Akana napui noyo, akana napui gama,
Misiṅ here horen senotan, hoyo dudugar ॥koṅ॥ 
 
 52 

Buido senotan bareṅ,
Nuli baṛa chetanete buido senotan ॥koṅ॥
Chiṭṭi kulai ben bareṅ,
Nuli mata dipilaṅ chiṭṭi kulaiben ॥koṅ॥
Kaben chiṭṭi kulai redo bareṅ,
Kuṭi nuli subareń tol gojenah ॥koṅ॥॥2 
 
 53 

Nale disum dona misiṅ,
Jol beṛa gea misiṅ jolajagada ॥koṅ॥॥
Nape disum doja misiṅ,
Rugut́ beṛa gea misiṅ ṭekora geaha ॥koṅ॥ 
 
 54 

Kuda nikir danḍika, chilikay,
Chili biliha kaben baṅṛasi ॥ koṅ॥
Daru chetan cheṅṛe menay, koto-kotoy,
Chal baṛana, kawen toṭhiha ॥koṅ॥ 
 
 55 

Dah do dah do, tentaṅ hintan,
Laido, laido, rengehiṅ tan,
Chimin saning reha repeṛeh, dahado namoha ॥koṅ॥2 
 
[13] 

Dah do namohago bareṅ,
Raja kore pukhuri dai do namoha ॥ koṅ ॥
Rani kore bandelare dah do namo ha
Nihatih geh sanaṅiṅ,
Chakatiṅ geh mohanĩya,
Raja kore pukhuri dah do ranjet́ jan ॥koṅ॥
Rani kore bandela dah do ranjet́ jan |k koṅ ॥ 
(bareṅ go) chimin mate seteṅ ha dah do ranjet́ jan ॥koṅ॥
Nesai sari, bah pari, chimin mate seteńa dahado
Ranjet́ jan ॥koṅ॥ 
 
 56 

Chetan pukhuri, latar pukhari,
Pan sakam doja bare lodobekena ॥koṅ॥
Diku non tan recham, pan dom jojoma ॥koṅ॥
Raja non tan recham, pan dom jojoma ॥koṅ॥॥
Nesai sari, bapari diku non tan recham
Pan dom jojoma ॥koṅ॥ 
 
 57 

Nengaṅy, napũy, menay redo,
Rumatulay, rumatulay, kaji seṭherah ॥koṅ॥
Nengaṅy, napũy, bangaya,
Rum tulay, rumatulay, kaji banoha ॥koṅ॥
Rumatulay, rumatulay kaji banoha ॥koṅ॥
Nehasari, kenajah, bale bareṅ ॥koṅ॥
Bapari, kenajai bale bareṅ ॥ 
 
 
[ 14] 
 
 58 

Nam doja munḍa nera,
Buru diri, noharado kam sesenah ॥koṅ॥
Saiu saga, noharado kam sesenah ॥
Nengam, napum, ṭhaikena,
Buru diri noharadom nuja pachuṛa ॥koṅ॥
Saiu saga noharadom, niraja sesenah ॥koṅ॥
Nesari kena jah bale bareṅ ॥koṅ॥
Bahapari kena jah ḍula misiṅ ॥koṅ॥ 
 
 59 

Meaḍege bale bareṅ, kinjiri raja,
Bheṭa bheṭa tewen dhira dhirana ॥koṅ॥
Bheṭa kiṅ chibin, kawen bheṭakiṅ ॥koṅ॥
Samaṛom ganḍu rikiṅ rakawejanah ॥koṅ॥
Nesai, sari, bahapari,
Samaṛom ganḍu rikiṅ rakawejana ॥ 
 
 60 

Thu non koaḱ turuiha, turuiha,
Sega non koaḱ moṛea moṛea, 
 Sirma janum jang chako jomatana,
Notereko le choṭe, leh choṭe॥ 
 
 61 

Naben doja bale bareṅ,
Ber benḍoṅ ber ber kawen nekelan ॥koṅ॥
Ṭoṅya tapa kel, kel,
Kaben nekelan ॥koṅ॥॥ 
 
[15] 

Dolaṅ seno hago bareṅ,
Dolaṅ biraḍago bareṅ
Berabenḍoṅ ber ber kaben nekelan ॥koṅ॥
Ṭoṅya tapa kel kel kawen nekelan ॥koṅ॥ 
 
 62 

Bandha kotem senoredo,
Noṛan kotem senoredo,
Salukat́ baṛa bareṅ, toṭaa daraṅy ben ॥koṅ॥
Kawen toṭaa daharaṅyado, kawen bheṭa daharaṅyado,
Munḍa koaḱ racha nuṭar baṛayaṅ,
Toṭagosoyaha ॥ koṅ॥
Kolam lekan, rachare,
Chiṛa bapaḍeh ॥koṅ॥॥
Nehasari kenajah bale bareṅ ॥ koṅ॥
Bahapari kenajah ḍula misĩ.॥koṅ॥ 
 
 63 

Barem racha poṛoso,
Nende sakam lena, punḍi, sakam-jana,
Sabin buginah ॥koṅ॥
Chetanete lipi, goh let́a,
Latarete noyo, goh let́a,
Johakan lipi, torosa, naṭa natuṛĩh ॥koṅ॥
Nesai sari, bahapari.
Johakan lipi, torosa, naṭa natuṛĩh ॥ koṅ॥ 
 
 64 

Sohaṛopo, soṛopote,
Ranchi soṛopote. 
 
[16] 

Gelabar sao, nomineko, bahalejanah ॥koṅ॥
Chinḍih koi biḍeha,
Durabin koaḱ neleha,
Danḍa koaḱ tamea,
Jinjirih koaḱ noh raha.
Muka, mukateko, seṭherelenah॥koṅ॥
Bita, bittateko, seṭherelenah ॥
Mongol mundhi(sihabhum) sima reko seṭherelenah ॥koṅ॥
Noṛo-noṛoheko panachaket́a ॥koṅ॥
Biga bigayahako ṭakayaheket́ah ॥koṅ॥2
Nihatihaṅ geh sanańi, chakatihaṅ geh mohanĩya,
Noṛo noṛo-heko, pana chaket́ah ॥koṅ॥
Biga bigayahako - ṭakayaheket́ah ॥ 
 
 65 

Bakaṛi jangi jangite,
Tiramitia karama kaluṭi natĩhetana ॥ koṅ॥
Naloreh chiru sanḍim keche kechenah ॥koṅ॥
Tiramitia karama kaluṭi natiṅ hetana ॥koṅ॥
Nerame nelangateh, doramo dolaṅ teh, dhoramo saṅṛi doy,
Karama kokotet́ ॥koṅ॥
Dharama kokotet́ ॥koṅ ॥ 
 
 66 

Nete putam ranado,
Diri richi, darureh guguchuḍũiha ॥koṅ ॥
Akana napui, diri,
Akana napui daru, 
 
 
[ 17] 

Jojoko, rumbulayareh guguchuḍuṅiha ॥koṅ॥
Nuli koaḱ rumwũlay reh guguchuḍũiha.
Bareṅ honaṅ menay redo, toṭhe gasar meha chahe diri putam ॥ koṅ॥
Tere goso meha, chahe, daru putam ॥koṅ॥
Nehasari kena jah bale bareṅ ॥koṅ॥
Bahapari kena jah ḍula misiṅ॥koṅ॥ 
 
 67 

Disumedo gule, gule, rajedo mele mele,
Disum chire, barengom nihatĩh tan ॥ koṅ॥
Neńaṅ mena recha bareṅ,
Disumedo bareṅ goy tinulemeha ॥koṅ॥
Napuṅ mena recha bareṅ,
Rajedo barengoy kulehemeha ॥koṅ॥ 
 
 68 

Bale singi tikin jana,
Bale chanḍua ponai jana,
Nukurihataṅy singabonga, seday napũi doh ॥koṅ॥
Nukurihataṅy singabonga, seday nengaṅy doh ॥
Chuilah kiṅ-senoy hana, chuilawano,
Nida reha kumu rikiṅ bageh ket́ीhaṅ ha ॥koṅ॥
Bheṭa kĩh gehaṅy metam,
Tewah kiń, gehaṅy metam,
