Mit́ bita laihabu nasuletanah ॥koṅ॥
Ká, seta, tuiyo, bana, neko gecha laidoko
Pereyetanah ॥koṅ॥ 
 
[ 35] 

Manami honabu, jonomakan,
Nekoyate chiminabu chetanakanah ॥koṅ॥
Napan sumat́ nuḍuntana,
Disum haga bugi doh kabu nuḍuṅ tan ॥koṅ॥ 2 
 
 125 

Disumatabu uttam mena, unati tabu chanaṕ mena,
Jete diku musolaman koaḱ ninda buhatana ॥koṅ॥
Karan-menateh torang, manus jonom namakete kabu
Nindana ॥koṅ॥॥
Aela tabu haga Hon koh,
Sangi tebu bichareha,
Chilaka leka teha tabu, disum rakawoh ॥koṅ॥
Siua habu, paiṭhi habu, nol paṛao netoyahabu,
Disum rakaboh ॥koṅ॥ 
 
 126 

Jili, mili bangalare,
Bidya, bandi nisukul reh,
Nokoy tikiṅ duṕ akan teh rasikatanah ॥koṅ॥
Rasikata nako metam,
Nol paṛao siṭhihako rasikatanah ॥koṅ॥
Nutum name, siṭhihako,
Bokasis name siṭhihako rasikatanah ॥koṅ॥ 2 
 
 127 

Nendor piṛi, piṛiteh,
Nipi piyuṅ, pipi piyuṅ, dongobekenah॥koṅ॥2
Akana napui, nipi piyuṅ, 
 
[ 36] 

Akana napui pipi piyuṅ,
Bale misihaṅ taṅyachana dongobekenah॥koṅ॥ 2 
 
 128 

Nelo tanam diku rani,
Landayawen mocho mocho,
Hay reh taṅy juṛing, daya chigo dhoramo banoha ॥koṅ॥2
Boṛo redo sohan sunum,
Mayaṅ redo gulaṕ saṛi,
Hay reh taṅy juṛing, daya chigo dhoramo banoha ॥koṅ॥ 2 
 
 129 

Bengon baṛi bitor reh,
Nana rokom baṛa juṛing koṛoṅ lenah ॥koṅ॥
Purubete, noyo let́a,
Pochimete noyo let́a,
Nana rokom, baṛa juṛing baṛa phuṭaw len ॥koṅ॥
Chiha tabu juṛing heko,
Chiha tabu nahagako,
Nòkon baṛa buginah, marabuh salayaha ॥koṅ॥ 2 
 130 

Jan kotem senoredo,
Jetan kotem senoredo,
Rupa reha penasil teh bondona tui ben॥koṅ॥ 2
Namageṅ nihatĩh metam ramachandr panḍit babu namageṅ
Nihatĩh ॥koṅ॥ 
 
 131 

Hoṛomo tam do mor leka,
Lija tam doh maraa pinchi, 
 
[ 37] 

Nam lekan sundar peari, kareṅ namiha॥koṅ॥ 2
Senen tam doh hõs leka,
Gun tam doh chondon daru,
Sita chire sawitrim, jonomelenah॥koṅ॥ 2
Siṭhia korem kajiyaḍĩh reh, nalo piritim metaṛĩh reh,
Nimin dukhu doh toraṅ kareṅ nameket́ ॥koṅ॥ 2
Naṅya ji doh loh tana,
Injin koyala leka pyari jih doh lotana ॥koṅ॥
Jiṛi ray lagit́ite,
Amrit kore piyus bindu tripi tuhaṅy ben॥koṅ॥2 
 
 132 

Boṛo balem tisar ket́a,
Maraa lekam singar jana,
Hayareh taṅy bale sundori kako gońe meh ॥koṅ॥
Bale mulua hoba lena. Chanḍua jaket́ nir jana,
Liṭhiṕ liṭhiṕ nomo reh
Samachigo pyari, samaṅy senotan ॥koṅ॥ 2
Nama juṛim namimeh,
Banteredo pyari sãsar reha sukhu karem nameha ॥koṅ॥ 2 
 
 133 

Hay goṛe taṅy sĩh boga,
Nimin dukhu disumere kaṭaṅe teka ket́ ॥koṅ॥
Chimitareṅ tega ket́a, chimitareṅ jonom lena,
Jonom nenga napu kiṅ bage natuḍĩh |k koṅ ॥
Bahu dada baṅ gaya,
Biti baba banoha, ॥
Sĩh bonga, namatr nuḍuṅ nuḍunteṅ nara maraṅg len ॥koṅ॥ 2 
 
[ 38] 
 
 134 

Nelo tanam komol baṛa,
Met́ muṭha chondon daru,
Chikateh mate bale somadoni, boṛo balem risa eana ॥koṅ॥
Choṅyabasa kore diroṅ naki,
Chakaṛa kore selaṭi arasi,
Sire sire bale somadoni,
Bale doh naki ben ॥koṅ॥ 2 
 
 135 

Kakasakam tinjhar bonjhor,
Chikan kili tanajam dinḍa somodi ॥koṅ॥
Kili hale somodi, nuduben meh ॥koṅ॥
Jati hale somodi jagarenameh ॥koṅ॥
Kili halem nudubenareh,
Jati halem jagaren reh,
Nale kili kili dole kili misameh ॥koṅ॥
Nale jati jati dole jati tala meh ॥ 
 
 136 

Chetan soṛopo latar soṛopo,
Somodi goṛe seno tan bangali moṭhor teh ॥koṅ॥
Sirajan prabhu sirajan(dhusaḱ)॥
Rong rumal, resom saṛi,
Diku kolom seno tan haṭa baṭa tan ॥koṅ॥ dhuḱ
Mocham joḍenago bareṅ,
Kili mili rumalete mocham joḍenaha.ko ॥ 2 
 
[ 36] 
 
 137 

Nuli go baṛa len somadi,
Tala goh masa koto reh nuligo baṛa len ॥koṅ॥ 2
Kae gamaeha, kay pukaḍeh,
Nuligo baṛa len ॥koṅ॥
Nuli mata samay somadi,
Dili kulaṅe ben somadi kaji kulaṅyaben
Kaben kaji kulaṅe redo,
Kaben dili kulaṅe redo,
Met́ mocha jaket́ somadi kareng nepelah ॥koṅ॥ 2 
 
 138 

Nesel berelagom somadi,
Belati nasalekam nasel berelah ॥koṅ॥
Naben sumat́ nago somadi,
Saranḍa birajooṅोl naben sumaḍah ॥koṅ॥
Tising bano, gapa bano,
Madukam leka somadi jiboneteben ॥koṅ॥2 
 
 136 

Nimin maraṅg prithbireh,
Chikanah metam saṛi tan disum dokol tan॥koṅ॥
Sri ramachandr dhonus ban, binaḍate disum dokolatan ॥koṅ ॥
Disum dokol jan reh,
Pharasadhari parasuram seṭherelenah ॥koṅ॥ 
 
 140 

Mihaḍege bale bareṅ, punḍi jota tegayameh bale bareṅ ॥koṅ॥
Singi biṛi tahalare, 
 
[ 40] 

Gor gobor disumere,
Diku kore numbul teh, numbulatu ben ॥koṅ॥
Raja kore chator teh, chatoratu ben ॥koṅ॥ 2 
 
 141 

Tiṛidom banadur basu,
Kaṭa dom banadur basu,
Kulakoh lekam neloha, nĩa doṅy boroyatan ॥koṅ॥
Menaṅy boroy tan somadi,
Singi chirem jomĩya, nidam jomiha ॥koṅ॥
Bareṅ honaṅ menay redo, toṛ toṛ topoṛeh toṭhe gasarameh.koṅ॥
Birala balaṅ, kaphi teh maa benḍo meh ॥koṅ॥ 2 
 
 142 

Bamonahaṭhi oṭharo piṛ "nochana,"
Chonadon bhonj raja projako dukhu tana ॥koṅ॥
Bicharako ben, nacharako ben "nochana"
Bhonj raja, dukhu sukhu, nisu bugin bicharako bena.
Munḍa koaḱ racha, komol baṛa,
Baṛayageh sanańiṅ nisu bugina,
Toṭhe geh sanańiṅ nisu bugina ॥koṅ॥ 
 
 143 

Namo somadi gaṛa parom,
Nĩo somadi nai parom,
Nauri hale dhonir beṭhi, misa telaṅa ha ॥koṅ॥ 2
Buru redo kula mena,
Gaṛa redo bĩa mena
Nauri hale dhonir beṭhi, misa telańa ॥koṅ॥ 
 
